headline: Hologic initiated with a Peer Perform at Wolfe amid near-term headwinds
summary: As previously reported, Wolfe Research analyst Doug Schenkel initiated coverage of Hologic (HOLX) with a Peer Perform rating and no price target The Diagnostics & Med Tech company caters to the healthcare and clinical end markets and the firm calls the company “an intriguing asset with a strong management team and unique portfolio.” However, while material downside risk is likely limited from here, the firm feels near term respiratory headwinds and saline shortages likely make expectations too h
